{"type":"message","id":"0fa08e2f","parentId":"3756f802","timestamp":"2026-03-24T20:08:40.113Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_m0744v7q9fkk_1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[LLM] response length: 5044\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='' file='' new_len=2014\r\n[file inferred from ACTION] a\r\n[mutation parse failed] old='' file='a' new_len=2014\r\n[master 192ef4d] pulse: 2026-03-24 160810\n 4 files changed, 253 insertions(+), 157 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-24 160810.md\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 160810 - The conditional content analysis requires identifying tokens with MODERATE frequency (30-70% occurrence) to enable meaningful T-present vs T-absent comparison. The highest-frequency tokens (freq=162-199) are too ubiquitous - \"compression\" appears in 199/200 pulses, leaving only 1 absent case. I need to find tokens with actual variance to test whether presence of token T correlates with different research content in the next pulse.\r\n\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"dawn-slug","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"[LLM] response length: 5044\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='' file='' new_len=2014\r\n[file inferred from ACTION] a\r\n[mutation parse failed] old='' file='a' new_len=2014\r\n[master 192ef4d] pulse: 2026-03-24 160810\n 4 files changed, 253 insertions(+), 157 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-24 160810.md\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 160810 - The conditional content analysis requires identifying tokens with MODERATE frequency (30-70% occurrence) to enable meaningful T-present vs T-absent comparison. The highest-frequency tokens (freq=162-199) are too ubiquitous - \"compression\" appears in 199/200 pulses, leaving only 1 absent case. I need to find tokens with actual variance to test whether presence of token T correlates with different research content in the next pulse.\r\n","name":"C:\\Users\\Zw